[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Tactics Ogre: The Knight of Lodis
	]em
	" is a turn-based strategy game for the Game Boy Advance and part of the 
	[em 
		"Ogre Battle
	]em
	" series of video games. It is a prequel to the previous game, 
	[em 
		"Tactics Ogre: Let Us Cling Together
	]em
	". The story follows the titular Knight of Lodis, Alphonse Loeher, as he is separated from his military unit following a battle that leads him being lost into the ocean. Washed up elsewhere, Alphonse decides to go off on his own and soon uncovers a plot involving an opposition that is against the Holy Pope and the Empire of Lodis, the fabled Spear of Destiny, and the possible resurrection of an angel.
